    strings.xml - String resources for the app

    All text displayed in the app should be defined here.
    Benefits:
    - Easy to translate to other languages
    - Change text without modifying code
    - Reuse strings across multiple screens

    For beginners: This is like a dictionary of all text in your app.
    Instead of hardcoding text in layouts, you reference strings from here.
-->
